  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AnswerDAO
    This is an interface that maps properties to fields of ANSWER table in database
    It is responsible for insert, update, delete and search Answer object in database
    QuestionDAO
    This is an interface that maps properties in this class to fields of QUESTION table in database
    It is responsible for insert, update, delete and search Question object in database
    QuestionSessionDAO
    This is an interface that maps properties in this file to fields of QUESTION_SESSION table in database
    It is responsible for insert, update, delete and search QuestionSession object in database
    QuestionTypeDAO
    This class is an interface mapping all properties in this class to fields of QUESTION_TYPE table in the database
    SessionDAO
    This class is an interface mapping all properties in this class to fields of SESSION table in the database
